        "task": "TASK: Analyse Issue Context and Produce Dual Output\n\nYou must analyse the issue and findings below, then produce a JSON response\nwith two sections: `customer_summary` and `developer_context`.\n\nYour output serves ONE PURPOSE: after reading it, a developer should UNDERSTAND\nthe task deeply before writing a single line of code. No guessing, no ambiguity.\n\n--- ISSUE CONTEXT ---\nTitle: TASK-5824 Angular Upgrade auf Version 19\nDescription: <p><a href=\"https://jira.bnotk.de/browse/UVZUSLNVV-5824\" class=\"external-link\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://jira.bnotk.de/browse/UVZUSLNVV-5824</a></p>\n\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n\n<p><b>AS-IS:</b></p>\n<ul>\n\t<li>UVZ currently uses 18 and PL 11.3.1</li>\n\t<li>The support for security updates did end on 21.11.2025 for Angular 18. The only option to get updates is via Never-Ending Support and payment, see <a href=\"https://endoflife.date/angular\" class=\"external-link\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://endoflife.date/angular</a> or <a href=\"https://www.herodevs.com/pricing\" class=\"external-link\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://www.herodevs.com/pricing</a>\u00a0</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n<p><b>Target:</b></p>\n<ul>\n\t<li>Upgrade to Angular 19 and PL 12.6.0</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n\n<p><b>Acceptance Criteria:</b></p>\n<ol>\n\t<li>UVZ is using Angular 19 and Pattern Library 12.6.0</li>\n\t<li>All necessary dependencies of acceptance criterion 1 are updated (for further information see comment from <a href=\"https://d3.ce.capgemini.com/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=fimisior\" class=\"user-hover\" rel=\"fimisior\">Filip Misiorek</a> for analysis <a href=\"https://d3.ce.capgemini.com/jira/browse/BNUVZ-12529?focusedId=4908577&amp;page=com.atlassian.jira.plugin.system.issuetabpanels:comment-tabpanel#comment-4908577\" class=\"external-link\" rel=\"nofollow\">\"how to get to angular 21\"</a>)\n\t<ul>\n\t\t<li>node.js</li>\n\t\t<li>typescript\u00a0</li>\n\t\t<li>bnotk/ds-ng</li>\n\t\t<li>ng-bootstrap (Patch von\u00a0<a href=\"https://jira.bnotk.de/browse/UVZUSLNVV-5824\" class=\"external-link\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">UVZUSLNVV-5824</a>\u00a0muss ber\u00fccksichtigt weerden)</li>\n\t\t<li>ng-select/ng-option-highlight</li>\n\t\t<li>ng-select/ng-select</li>\n\t\t<li>ag-grid-angular</li>\n\t\t<li>ag-grid-community</li>\n\t</ul>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>Vertical action bar is still being used (deprecated but still possible to use till PL 13.2.0. For more information see storyboard of DS)</li>\n\t<li>No longer needed or oudated parts of Angular 18 or Pattern Library 11.3.1 are no longer part of UVZ. Exception: these parts are still required and supported by Angular 19 and PL 12.6.0.</li>\n</ol>\n\n\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Original German description:</p>\n\n<p><b>Ist:</b></p>\n<ul>\n\t<li>UVZ verwendet aktuell Angular 18 und PL 11.3.1</li>\n\t<li>Der Security-Support f\u00fcr Angular 18 ist am 21.11.2025 abgelaufen. Es gibt nur noch die M\u00f6glichkeit gegen Bezahlung via Never-Ending Support updates zu bekommen, siehe\u00a0<a href=\"https://endoflife.date/angular\" class=\"external-link\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://endoflife.date/angular</a>\u00a0bzw.\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.herodevs.com/pricing\" class=\"external-link\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://www.herodevs.com/pricing</a>\u00a0</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n<p><b>Soll:</b></p>\n<ul>\n\t<li>Upgrade auf Angular 19 und PL 12.6.0</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n\n<p><b>Akzeptanzkriterien:</b></p>\n<ol>\n\t<li>UVZ verwendet Angular 19 und Pattern Library 12.6.0</li>\n\t<li>Alle n\u00f6tigen Abh\u00e4ngigkeiten werden gem\u00e4\u00df Akzeptanzkriterium Nr. 1 geupdated:\n\t<ul>\n\t\t<li>node.js</li>\n\t\t<li>typescript\u00a0</li>\n\t\t<li>bnotk/ds-ng</li>\n\t\t<li>ng-bootstrap (Patch von\u00a0<a href=\"https://jira.bnotk.de/browse/UVZUSLNVV-5824\" class=\"external-link\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">UVZUSLNVV-5824</a>\u00a0muss ber\u00fccksichtigt weerden)</li>\n\t\t<li>ng-select/ng-option-highlight</li>\n\t\t<li>ng-select/ng-select</li>\n\t\t<li>ag-grid-angular</li>\n\t\t<li>ag-grid-community</li>\n\t</ul>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>Es wird nach wie vor die vertikale Aktionsleiste verwendet (deprecated aber noch bis einschlie\u00dflich PL 13.2.0 im Storybook verf\u00fcgbar)</li>\n\t<li>Es befinden sich keine alten Bestandteile von Angular 18 oder Pattern Library 11.3.1 mehr in UVZ, au\u00dfer diese werden von Angular 19 und PL 12.6.0 verwendet und supported.</li>\n</ol>\n\n\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<hr />\n<p><b>Originale Anforderung:</b></p>\n\n<p>Hallo,</p>\n\n<p>das UVZ nutzt aktuell die Angular Version 18. Die Version 18 ist bereits Deprecated und nicht mehr supported.</p>\n\n<p>Daher m\u00fcssen wir in einem ersten Schritt auf Angular 19 updaten. Wie im FRM am 14.01.26 besprochen, das wir nicht direkt auf 20 oder 21 gehen k\u00f6nnen.<br/>\nQuelle:\u00a0<a href=\"https://angular.dev/reference/versions\" class=\"external-link\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://angular.dev/reference/versions</a></p>\n\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n\n<p>Vielen Dank</p>\nPriority: Major\n--- END ISSUE CONTEXT ---\n\n--- SUPPLEMENTARY CONTEXT (requirements, logs) ---\n(none)\n--- END SUPPLEMENTARY ---\n\n--- DETERMINISTIC FINDINGS ---\n{\n  \"classification\": {\n    \"type\": \"refactor\",\n    \"confidence\": 0.99,\n    \"signals\": [\n      \"keyword:upgrade\"\n    ],\n    \"scores\": {\n      \"bug\": 0.0,\n      \"feature\": 0.0,\n      \"refactor\": 1.0,\n      \"investigation\": 0.0\n    }\n  },\n  \"entry_points\": [],\n  \"blast_radius\": {\n    \"affected\": [],\n    \"depth\": 0,\n    \"component_count\": 0,\n    \"containers_affected\": []\n  },\n  \"duplicates\": [\n    {\n      \"chunk_id\": \"f1352537:0000:b6f07307\",\n      \"path\": \"\",\n      \"score\": 0.742,\n      \"snippet\": \"VVZ - Testdaten EDU-Umgebung\\n============================\\n\\nLieferumfang