st them.)\n  - Java 17 (language) \u2014 source: tech_versions.json\n  - Gradle 8.2.1 (build_tool) \u2014 source: tech_versions.json\n  - TypeScript 4.9.5 (language) \u2014 source: tech_versions.json\n  - Playwright 1.43.1 (library) \u2014 source: tech_versions.json\n  - Angular 18.2.13 (framework) \u2014 source: tech_versions.json\n  - Angular CLI 18.2.19 (build_tool) \u2014 source: tech_versions.json\n  - RxJS 7.4.0 (library) \u2014 source: tech_versions.json\n  - Webpack 5.80.0 (build_tool) \u2014 source: tech_versions.json\n  - Karma 6.4.3 (library) \u2014 source: tech_versions.json\n  - Cypress 14.0.3 (library) \u2014 source: tech_versions.json\n\n=== ANALYSIS INPUT: Dependencies (runtime) ===\n(What LIBRARY RISKS exist? Version conflicts, deprecations?)\n  - @types/chai-arrays ^2.0.3 (npm) \u2014 source: dependencies.json\n  - chai-arrays ^2.2.0 (npm) \u2014 source: dependencies.json\n  - edge-js ^21.7.4 (npm) \u2014 source: dependencies.json\n  - log-timestamp ^0.3.0 (npm) \u2014 source: dependencies.json\n  - playwright ~1.43.1 (npm) \u2014 source: dependencies.json\n  - @angular/animations 18.2.13 (npm) \u2014 source: dependencies.json\n  - @angular/common 18.2.13 (npm) \u2014 source: dependencies.json\n  - @angular/compiler 18.2.13 (npm) \u2014 source: dependencies.json\n  - @angular/core 18.2.13 (npm) \u2014 source: dependencies.json\n  - @angular/forms 18.2.13 (npm) \u2014 source: dependencies.json\n\n=== ANALYSIS INPUT: Error Handling ===\n(What error handling patterns MUST be followed?)\n  - InvalidAuthenticationTokenException:  \u2014 source: error_handling.json\n  - PkiCardRequiredException:  \u2014 source: error_handling.json\n  - DefaultExceptionHandler.handleException:  \u2014 source: error_handling.json\n  - DefaultExceptionHandler.duplicateIdException:  \u2014 source: error_handling.json\n  - DefaultExceptionHandler.httpClientErrorExceptionHandler:  \u2014 source: error_handling.json\n\n=== ANALYSIS INPUT: Architecture Overview ===\n(What is the